c: 57
v: 14
t: "(Those hypocrites outside) will call the believers, \"Were we not with you?\" (The others) will reply, \"True! But you led yourselves into temptation; You looked forward (to our destruction); And you doubted (Allah’s Promise); And (your false) desires deceived you; Until the Command of Allah became true. And the Deceiver (Satan) deceived you in respect to (Almighty) Allah"